{"id": 1103, "genre": 1001, "title": "你会认可哪些“诚意”？", "description": "大家一起心连心，多么怡人的商业模式！（题图来自：Yuki Kitazumi）", "record_count": 4393, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607102241111Wk6UwEIVdZJLPyO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-16T22:57:23Z", "options": [{"id": 99328, "content": "薛之谦：说了这么多，总之，我的新专辑大家就别买了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682397}, {"id": 100352, "content": "道谢的时候说   谢谢你   而不是说 谢谢！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685061}, {"id": 99329, "content": "忙到不能回复是先告诉我再去忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634400}, {"id": 99331, "content": "餐馆点菜时候主动告诉你WiFi密码。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673230}, {"id": 99332, "content": "就是不要锁区?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 577198}, {"id": 99333, "content": "老板认可你的能力，却不加薪！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109759}, {"id": 100102, "content": "正片和预告片一样好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259260}, {"id": 100103, "content": "正品和小样一样好用", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259260}, {"id": 99336, "content": "打球时撞你能抱住你别让你摔倒的", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468474}, {"id": 137482, "content": "直接打折，不要满减", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689742}, {"id": 99084, "content": "售后和售前一样好", "image": null, "praise_count": 635, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293164}, {"id": 99340, "content": "手机只有一个内存版本", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682410}, {"id": 99086, "content": "不突兀的，走心的广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 142, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 12364}, {"id": 99342, "content": "付过款还当我是回事儿?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682412}, {"id": 99087, "content": "客服有礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219172}, {"id": 99343, "content": "同学不会不耐烦地给我讲题，即使耽搁他们自己的时间也会给我讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679127}, {"id": 99088, "content": "不卖弄情怀，但做到口口相传", "image": null, "praise_count": 225, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391490}, {"id": 100624, "content": "面试前一天晚上，HR会用手机在下班之后打电话告诉你该准备什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688252}, {"id": 99089, "content": "买东西时，不想见人的时候没有人，想付钱的时候人来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 323, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680559}, {"id": 100113, "content": "改稿不到半夜不发，白天就补觉找不到人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685978}, {"id": 99090, "content": "应用里没有过分的广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628393}, {"id": 99091, "content": "洗头发时不推荐办卡！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 259, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644001}, {"id": 99347, "content": "听你别人说话时，能够注视别人，不看手机和打呵欠", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682030}, {"id": 99093, "content": "言行一致，一诺千金。", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652338}, {"id": 99349, "content": "不愛我早説，寧願你一早便不給予我希望", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623124}, {"id": 99094, "content": "真正愿意分享人生经验，不把教育只当作自己的职场的老师", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680621}, {"id": 99095, "content": "点菜的时候会告诉你吃不吃的完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 623, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227996}, {"id": 99098, "content": "包裹里有张卖家手写的卡片", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115257}, {"id": 99356, "content": "音乐不必付费", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675196}, {"id": 99357, "content": "苹果自带越狱版本", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675196}, {"id": 99102, "content": "买橘子告诉我是酸的", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529504}, {"id": 99358, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330161}, {"id": 99103, "content": "拒绝的时候不发好人卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199459}, {"id": 99104, "content": "心机表的两面性", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617678}, {"id": 99105, "content": "不用充会员", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601788}, {"id": 99361, "content": "少点套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680656}, {"id": 99106, "content": "解决问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674760}, {"id": 99362, "content": "遇到贱人 颠倒是非 不知道该怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682467}, {"id": 99107, "content": "不说“我们不合适”，不在分手以后说“我还喜欢你”，“祝你幸福”…", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680358}, {"id": 99363, "content": "买衣服时就算不买临走前店家也会好言好语", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 106232}, {"id": 99364, "content": "爱吃甜食 是因为心里苦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682467}, {"id": 99366, "content": "剪头发的时候 根据脸型设计 不乱推销", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572313}, {"id": 99111, "content": "食品恪守安全", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681699}, {"id": 99367, "content": "进门的第一个微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296381}, {"id": 106793, "content": "不做作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711860}, {"id": 99114, "content": "不买也不会黑脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 319, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681705}, {"id": 99115, "content": "点菜的时候，服务员告诉我，已经够了，不要点太多，会吃不完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681711}, {"id": 99371, "content": "没有套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511564}, {"id": 99116, "content": "用心做事 工匠精神 为了作品 放弃盈利", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681709}, {"id": 99373, "content": "话不要太多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680873}]}